controller

Class AddNewPhotoController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.AddNewPhotoController

  • public class AddNewPhotoController
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages the procedure to add a new photo to an album. Displays the options to add, delete, or edit a tag in order to construct a tag list that is given to the photo object.
    Author:
    Omar Khalil, Michelle Hwang
